      The Glenn Beck Radio Program - 12/9/13Monday, December 09, 2013 10:45 AM



Glenn and the gang are snowed in but still live and laying out the global warming fallacy,
   because according to many global warming should have gotten rid of all snow by now.

  Also, the TSA have gone too far, by seizing a woman's sock monkey from her sewing bag.

  Thanks TSA for protecting us from those dangerous sock monkeys.

  Plus, apparently the Obama administration is structuring a secret trade deal
      to give corporations radical new political power.
